@Node "DESIGN_TASYS" "TASys - The Famous Digital Design! - (C) S.Gillibrand 1995 - Digital Design"

What/Who is Digital Design
+------------------------+

Digital Design is a group of people who code all types of programmes for BBSs
around the world, TransAmiga, DLG, Xeno, ANY Basically.

It was founded by @{"Stuart Gillibrand" Link "AUTHOR_TASYS"} in February 1995.


         President: Stuart Gillibrand - scatman@digitald.demon.co.uk
         Vice President: Jamie Prince - cosysop@digitald.demon.co.uk

Programmers:                                       ANSI Artists:
 Stuart Gillibrand                                  Stuart Gillibrand
 Jamie Prince                                       Jamie Prince


Documentation writers:                             Ideas:
 Stuart Gillibrand                                  Stuart Gillibrand
 Jamie Prince                                       Jamie Prince


If you would like to join Digital Design as a Programmer, Doc Writer, Artist
or Idea Conceptor (?!) then contact @{"ME" Link "AUTHOR_TASYS"}.

We ONLY accept programming in the languages:

Arexx, C, E and ASM.

You will need to show us an example of your skill if you wish to join, which
both Jamie and I will look over before contacting you.

@EndNode
